name: DataStore
description: The DataStore is shortest described as BigDataServer that can also accept images besides serving them. In other words, it is a REST HTTP-based client-server for downloading/uploading chunks from images from/to a remote dataset. The server is storing image data using the N5 on disk in a BigDataViewer unique XML/N5 dialect. The server communicates with its clients using our own simple protocol.
